// Lootbox Endpoints

### Get All Lootboxes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes

### Get Lootbox by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/1

### Get Lootbox by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/99999

### Get Lootbox by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/invalid

### Get Player's Lootboxes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/lootboxes

### Get Player's Lootboxes (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/lootboxes

### Create Lootbox
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "purchase"
}

### Create Lootbox (free)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "free"
}

### Create Lootbox (reward)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "reward"
}

### Create Lootbox (invalid acquiredHow)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "invalid"
}

### Create Lootbox (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1
}

### Open Lootbox
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/open
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "free"
}

### Open Lootbox (invalid acquiredHow)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/open
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxTypeId": 1,
    "playerId": 1,
    "acquiredHow": "invalid"
}

### Open Lootbox (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/open
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1
}

### Delete Lootbox
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/1

### Delete Lootbox (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootboxes/99999


// LootboxType Endpoints

### Get All Lootbox Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types

### Get Available Lootbox Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/available

### Get Lootbox Type by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/1

### Get Lootbox Type by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/99999

### Create Lootbox Type
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Premium Crate",
    "description": "High chance for rare items",
    "costCoins": 500,
    "costFree": false,
    "dailyLimit": 3,
    "isAvailable": true
}

### Create Lootbox Type (free)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Daily Free Box",
    "description": "Free daily lootbox",
    "costCoins": 0,
    "costFree": true,
    "dailyLimit": 1,
    "isAvailable": true
}

### Create Lootbox Type (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Incomplete Type"
}

### Update Lootbox Type
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Crate",
    "costCoins": 750
}

### Update Lootbox Type Availability
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/1/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "isAvailable": false
}

### Delete Lootbox Type
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/1

### Delete Lootbox Type (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/99999

### Count Lootbox Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-types/count


// LootboxDrop Endpoints

### Get All Lootbox Drops
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops

### Get Lootbox Drop by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/1

### Get Lootbox Drop by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/99999

### Get Drop by Lootbox ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/lootbox/1

### Get Drop by Stove ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/stove/1

### Get Player's Lootbox Drops
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/lootbox-drops

### Create Lootbox Drop
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxId": 1,
    "stoveId": 1
}

### Create Lootbox Drop (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stoveId": 1
}

### Delete Lootbox Drop
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/1

### Delete Lootbox Drop (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/99999

### Count Lootbox Drops
GET http://localhost:3000/api/lootbox-drops/count
